31323.name: Liquid Touch Weightless Foundation
31323.benefits: This super fluid, serum-like texture makes it easy to build and blend your coverage just how you like it while evening out skin tone and smoothing the look of pores—no clogging or caking. Plus, the mess-free, doe-foot applicator lets you apply 1 dot at a time—all you need to cover your entire face. The formula helps soothe, calm, and nourish skin with a botanical blend of lotus, gardenia, and white water lily.
31323.description: An innovative breathable foundation that combines the weightless feel of a serum with buildable medium coverage for truly layerable wear.
31323.how-to:
* This foundation is best suited for normal and combination skin.
* If you have dry skin, it is recommended to prep your skin with a hydrating moisturizer and then follow with Always an Optimist Primer (sold separately) for best results.
* If you have oily skin, it is recommended to use our Always an Optimist Pore Diffusing Primer (sold separately) and/or set your foundation with a powder.
* Shake well before each use to ensure the foundation pigments are evenly dispersed throughout.
* Because of its innovative, serum-like formula, pressing the foundation into your skin with fingertips is encouraged but feel free to use the Liquid Touch Foundation Brush or a damp sponge.
* Start with the smallest amount needed—it’s recommended to use just 1 dot of foundation for the entire face. Use fingertips to blend in circular or tapping motions to press formula into the skin; the warmth of your fingertips will allow the pigments to melt into your skin for the best results.
* If you are using a brush or sponge, blend or stipple the foundation until it looks and feels like skin.
* For more coverage, add another dot and build as desired.
* This foundation has concentrated pigments so less is more—add a second layer only where needed.

42115.name: HD Skin Powder Foundation
42115.benefits: No one wants a compact foundation to be cakey and powdery. That's why HD Skin Powder Foundation provides full coverage, comfort and blur in a breathable, natural formula. This foundation corrects, blurs and mattifies for up to 24 hours thanks to a combination of 3 different powders and covers redness and freckles in just one swipe while at the same time refining the pores and evening out skin texture.
42115.description: An undetectable compact foundation that gives you a matte finish and blur in only one swipe.
42115.how-to:
* For a truly second skin effect, apply with the soft side of the sponge, from the centre of the face blending outwards with dabbing motions.
* For a softer and more natural look, blend with the fluffy side of the sponge, with swiping motions.
* For a more natural finish or touch up: use brush #128 all over the face.
* Pro tips: Use as a lid primer on oily lids or after liquid foundation with a brush to set your makeup.

Your multitasking beauty miracle provides clinically tested hydration while diffusing the look of skin imperfections for flawless-looking coverage that won’t crease or crack.
18878.how-to:

* It can be used as your foundation, concealer, anti-ageing serum, moisturiser and sunscreen, based on your coverage needs.
* For best results, apply a smooth, even layer to your face, neck and decollete for complexion perfection.

36430.name: HD Skin Foundation
36430.benefits: HD Skin Foundation has been co-created with professionals to give buildable, medium to full foundation coverage for a semi-matte yet natural finish. It’s ideal for normal, combination or oily skins and corrects and blurs imperfections for 24 hours. The foundation is undetectable thanks to the very first micro-skin system that syncs with the skin, meaning no cracks and no dry patches. Available in 40 shades, there's an option for every skin tone.
36430.description: A new foundation for flawless skin with an ultra-natural finish and colours for up to 24 hours of wear.
36430.how-to:
* Apply with the HD Skin brush 109 or with the bi material sponge.
* If you have a normal to combination skin, use #Step 1 Hydra Booster to hydrate your skin, then to unify your complexion use HD councealer and HD Skin Foundation. Finish with Ultra HD micro finishing loose powder and a few sprays of Mist Fix to set your make up.
* If you have a normal to oily skin, use #Step 1 Shine Control to refine your skin texture, then to unify your complexion use HD councealer and HD Skin Foundation. Finish with Ultra HD Setting powder and a few sprays of Light Velvet air to set your make up.
* Start at the centre of your face and apply stroking outwards, blending it onto the ears (if there is redness or if the hair is pulled back).
* Avoid applying foundation on the eyes area (on the eyelid or under the eyes) as this can accentuate signs of ageing or fatigue.
* Continue with the chin and the facial contour.
* Finish by applying the product to the forehead, blending it up.

28248.name: Pro Filt'r Soft Matte Powder Foundation
28248.benefits:
- Longwear, light-as-air, no flashback
- Blur Filt’r complex to deliver the ultimate, blurred finish
- Sweat-, humidity-, and crease-resistant
- Buildable, light to full coverage formula that loves to be layered
- Won’t settle into fine lines, clog pores or cake up
- Reduces the appearance of shine
- Chic, portable powder compact fits in hand
Did you know?!
Rihanna loves poreless, blurred-looking skin but could never find the perfect powder to satisfy her needs. After 3 years of perfecting this formula, she developed the ultimate powder that makes skin look like skin, not cakey, and works on all skin types and tones. It’s the perfect filter on the go and she always has this in her purse.
28248.description: The award-winning foundation that forever changed the game, now in a longwear, light-as-air powder to deliver light to full coverage in a non-cakey soft matte finish in 50 shades for all. It’s fast, flawless, easy.
28248.how-to:
Prep: Before applying Pro Filt’r Soft Matte Powder Foundation, be sure to moisturize skin with Fenty Skin Hydra Vizor Invisible Moisturizer Broad Spectrum SPF 30 Sunscreen.
• After moisturizing, apply your favorite Pro Filt’r primer and let set for best results.
• Use the included sponge to build to your desired coverage for a flawless, blurred finish. We recommend the Powder Puff Setting Brush 170 for light coverage. For medium to full coverage, apply using the Kabuki Buff Brush.
Pro Tip: The looser the brush, the lighter the coverage.
Rihanna’s Way: Apply on top of your Pro Filt’r liquid foundation for added coverage on the go.
SHADE FINDING TIPS:
- Pro Filt’r Soft Matte Powder Foundation comes in the same 50 shades as the original Pro Filt’r so if you know your shade # start there and adjust as needed—you may need to go a shade lighter.
- Don’t know your shade #? Start with your shade range (Light, Light Medium, Medium Deep, Deep), then narrow down your skin’s undertone. For more help, try our Fenty Face Shade Finder.

12180.name: Pro Filt'r Soft Matte Longwear Foundation
12180.benefits: This buildable, medium to full coverage foundation gives skin an instantly smooth, pore-diffused, shine-free finish. After doing extensive consumer testing and rigorous research, we refreshed our shade range to give y’all the most inclusive 50 shades yet.
12180.description: A soft matte, longwear foundation with climate-adaptive technology to fight to heat, sweat + shine—available in 50 shades.
12180.how-to:
Be sure to prep skin with Fenty Skin Hydra Vizor SPF 15 Moisturizer before applying foundation, especially if your skin is dry. After moisturizing, prep skin with Pro Filt’r Instant Retouch Primer to smooth the look of pores and absorb shine, for smoother foundation application and extended makeup wear.

Always shake before use to activate. When testing shades, remember to let matte foundations dry completely to find your perfect match.

For full coverage: Apply 1-2 pumps of Pro Filt’r Foundation on the back of your hand. Using the Full-Bodied Foundation Brush 110, dot product onto the center of your face and blend outward.

For medium, customizable coverage: Apply 1 pump of Pro Filt’r Foundation to the back of your hand. Using a damp Precision Makeup Sponge 100, begin applying product at the center of your face, or wherever coverage is desired, pressing foundation into skin and blending outward. 

RIHANNA’S WAY: For the ultimate pore coverage, press the  Full-Bodied Foundation Brush 110 into skin, roll off, and repeat.

20398.name: Your Skin But Better CC+ Cream SPF 50 Mini
20398.benefits: This cream is your one-stop for colour-correcting full foundation coverage, anti-ageing benefits and SPF 50 UVA/UVB broad-spectrum protection. Developed with plastic surgeons, your best-selling, award-winning beauty miracle delivers clinically tested hydration. It also delivers seven products all in one, from full-coverage foundation, brightening colour corrector, hydrating and anti-ageing serum, poreless finish primer, dark spot concealer to SPF 50 UVA/UVB broad-spectrum protection. Infused with hydrolysed collagen, peptides, niacin, hyaluronic acid, antioxidants and vitamins, this multitasking makeup product is truly your must-have for instant complexion perfection.
20398.description: A CC+ cream with SPF 50 that hydrates your skin while diffusing the appearance of imperfections for flawless-looking coverage that won't crease or crack.
20398.how-to:
* Apply 1-2 pumps to clean skin using your favourite brush.
* Can be used as your foundation, concealer, anti-ageing serum, moisturiser and sunscreen, based on your coverage needs.
* For best results, apply a smooth, even layer to your face, neck and decollete.

42107.name: Good Apple Full-Coverage Transfer-Proof Vegan Serum Foundation
42107.benefits: This full-coverage foundation visibly blurs pores and stands up to sweat and humidity without clogging pores. Packed with flexible elastomer pigments, it blends and bends with your skin for a seamless, flashback-free finish that covers everything from blemishes to acne scars, hyperpigmentation, and more.
42107.description: A full-coverage natural finish foundation with transfer-proof extreme wear and a serum-light feel.
42107.how-to:
* Fully Custom Coverage: Shake well before each use. Use a sponge to tap Good Apple into skin and build up to whatever level of coverage you want. Use a dense foundation brush with a buffing motion for more immediate full coverage.
* Pump It Up: 1 pump for buildable full coverage, 2+ pumps for instant full coverage.
* Prep & Set: Press Lock-It Pore-Refining Primer into the skin before applying your foundation to reduce the look of pores, focusing on areas where your pores are most visible. Lightly dust on Lock-It Setting Powder for a blurred, silky-smooth finish that removes oily shine.
* Once your Good Apple foundation bottle is fully empty, discard the pump and cap, then toss the glass bottle in the recycling. Check with your local recycling facility for any restrictions.
